  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge Together is a relaxing two-player puzzle game where strategic thinking, harmony, and teamwork are key. Players aim to combine sweet fruits, level by level, to achieve larger fruits and ultimately reach the final goal: the watermelon.<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple and accessible mechanics, Merge Together enhances teamwork and communication through its two-player mode, creating a fun, competitive experience with friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a28c6e5bd.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a28c6e5bd.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a28c6e5bd.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring colorful, delightful visuals and a soothing atmosphere, the game delivers a unique experience each time. As you progress, Merge Together offers both challenging puzzles and an enjoyable time. Its smooth gameplay makes each move exciting, keeping the joy of the game alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0a2e53b370ddc0785ed21e224729fa70.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0a2e53b370ddc0785ed21e224729fa70.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0a2e53b370ddc0785ed21e224729fa70.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge Together is a relaxing two-player puzzle game where strategic thinking, harmony, and teamwork are key. Players aim to combine sweet fruits, level by level, to achieve larger fruits and ultimately reach the final goal: the watermelon.<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple and accessible mechanics, Merge Together enhances teamwork and communication through its two-player mode, creating a fun, competitive experience with friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a